{"tid":1422132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好唔記得扯裙事件","createTime":"2019-08-06T09:54:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T11:23:02.000Z","uid":167176,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"35a9144386d787c11b8d51002304f87e5ec071f0","tid":1422132,"uid":167176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:54:01.000Z","msg":"雖然事主講咗自己嘅情況已經okay <br />\n但香港人其實真係會好善忘，好快唔記得<br />\n而且香港黑社會做嘅野越黎越過份<br />\n慢慢人就會開始淡化、合理化事件<br />\n我要大家記住香港警察唔只係黑社會，仲係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">強姦犯</span>。<br />\n侮辱女性、侵犯人權，絕不能容忍！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢單野，我地必須追究到底！！<br />\n<br />\n唔好唔記得天水圍仲要搵咗幾十人！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">強姦犯</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑社會</span>"},{"pid":"38d7c43f643e0a8cc76b2ce980365f4efb6d67b0","tid":1422132,"uid":167176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:54:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"056bc5e49fc2158d9b0d71ed0fe95e23ba5c59dc","tid":1422132,"uid":167176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:54:28.000Z","msg":"有冇人dm咗女權係有回覆"},{"pid":"788ddb237ea388fa7af9655ddf52ea7478933b22","tid":1422132,"uid":167176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:54:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e24d264c9b9f121c7fba8826453c21146f0a83a","tid":1422132,"uid":167176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:54:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d294c81adb7377a74256d3544b3c91b22ba545a7","tid":1422132,"uid":167176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:55:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"828f122e8ac24b8a9a57b50f6f516cee760d8bfe","tid":1422132,"uid":167176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:55:33.000Z","msg":"停止侮辱女性"},{"pid":"cdfa7003d8fe5d9953ed27b9e635382a8bc4694a","tid":1422132,"uid":167176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:55:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f6e5645812720301a823b6c9f812d59dc018d10"